  "2026-07-19T06:08:01.653Z",maintainer-agent,"Greptile findings resolved with regression coverage: bulk repair now preserves per-stream reconciliation reports and prefixed warnings; empty JSON sides emit valid null; malformed managed fences are normalized without duplicate markers; Git passes %P so Markdown format detection does not depend on temp-file extensions. Focused 119 tests, typecheck, and contract checks pass."
